meta.title: Caillou Temper Tantrum Over Corn On the Cob

ttsdata.text: What are we having for dinner?
Corn? No thank you. I'm okay, I don't want any corn.
No! I don't want any corn! Corn is yucky.
KAI U, your father said you need to eat corn. Eat it now or you will be grounded.
Fine, I'll eat the stinky corn. I really hate corn though.
Oh, it looks like KAI U still has some on his plate.
Daddy, I'm not a baby, stop treating me like one! I don't want your fucking corn!
You know what, curse your corn! Here's what I think of your shitty corn!
I'm sorry dad, I'll eat the corn on the cob on the floor. Then we can go to Chuck E Cheeses.
I'm going to sneak downstairs to get some cookies to take to bed.
Oh no, I have to walk quietly so daddy doesn't catch me.
Wow! Bag of cookies! I'm going to just take a few upstairs.
Darn it, I can't reach them.
Wait, my daddy has a ladder in his garage. I'll use that to climb up.
Ha ha ha ha ha ha
Yay, a stepladder.
Ooof, this is heavy.
I'm, almost, there. Just, a, little, more, to, go.
Sleepy.
Oh, good morning dad. Wait, what the? Why am I? Oh. Uh oh.
Well you see, last night, I heard these voices, and uh, I saw these two monsters. Um, not monsters.
Robbers. They were robbers. And they were in the kitchen.
So I blocked them with the ladder here. I kinda saved the day.
Yay, he doesn't know what happened.
Ha ha, yeah. I guess we both joked with each other. So, we're equal huh?
Wah wah wah wah wah wah wah wah.
Wait, he never said I couldn't eat the cookies. He just grounded me for sneaking out of my room.
Time to have a yummy breakfast for a change.
Oh my god, those were so good.
What the?
I'm a fat ass.
Ow, my tummy hurts. I have to go to the bathroom.
I can barely get up.
I just, need to, walk a bit, further.
Why do I keep farting?
Oh my god, I have to go so bad.
